Astilabor Hoardmistress is the draconic desire to acquire treasure and power. She is neutral, and dislikes the naked greed displayed by Tiamat and Task. She is revered by dragons of every species, manifesting as a huge dragon that shimmers with all the chromatic and metallic colors of dragonkind. Her Realm in Limbo is said to contain more wealth than that found in all the planets of the Material+Plane.
She is friendly toward Moradin and Garl Glittergold, but dislikes Olidammara.
Sources: 2e Draconomicon, Cult of the Dragon, 3e Draconomicon, Races of the Dragon